    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to provide an exceptional power-to-weight ratio. The drivetrain features a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to manage torsional stress. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings, ensuring precise turn-in and minimal body roll. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle mapping are dialed in for peak performance. A mechanically robust example for the purist.",
