    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Audi Q7 3.0T Premium Plus is a meticulously maintained luxury SUV that perfectly balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior is finished in a deep Moonlight Blue Metallic that retains a brilliant luster, complemented by 20-inch 10-spoke-star design wheels. While the body is in great shape, there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear bumper from standard use. Inside, the cabin features Nougat Brown leather upholstery that is clean and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. This vehicle is equipped with the Cold Weather Package, including a heated steering wheel and rear seats, and the Bose 3D Surround Sound System for an immersive audio experience. Mechanically, the 333-hp supercharged V6 runs smoothly, and the Quattro all-wheel-drive system provides exceptional stability. I have kept a detailed log of all oil changes and filter replacements. The tires are in great condition with plenty of life left, and the brakes are responsive. It is a smoke-free, reliable vehicle that presents beautifully and is ready for its next journey.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
